// pan card = aadhar card link (new)

way 1:

You have to type a message in the format.
UIDPAN<12 Digit Aadhaar> <10 Digit PAN>
Send the message to either 567678 or 56161 from your registered mobile number

example:

If your Aadhaar number is 987654321012 and your PAN is ABCDE1234F, 
you have to type UIDPAN 987654321012 ABCDE1234F and send the message to either 567678 or 56161

